		<title>12LAW AND ORDER</title>
		<content> There is no police station in the     
 village of Glyncorrwg. There is a     
 police house which was built in 1980  
 but this is empty and is only used by 
 the police on Saturdays for two hours 
 when people can make complaints or    
 give information.The nearest police   
 station is in Cymmer two and a half   
 miles away but any calls to the police
 must be directed to Port Talbot twelve
 miles away. The nearest Magistrates   
 Court is in Port Talbot and the       
 nearest Crown Court is in Swansea.    
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
